title: (Weds Full) Bobby on Eric Church Cancelling His Concert To Go To Final Four + Why Lunchbox Thinks The World Is Ending + Unfortunate Haunted Doll Update
itunes:title: (Weds Full) Bobby on Eric Church Cancelling His Concert To Go To Final Four + Why Lunchbox Thinks The World Is Ending + Unfortunate Haunted Doll Update
description:
Bobby talks about how people are upset at Eric Church for cancelling his concert in San Antonio to attend the Final Four instead. He puts himself into the situation on if he’d do the same…. Lunchbox thinks the world is ending because of something he saw going down this week. We get an update on the Creepy Doll that the show member has to take home…and it’s not looking good.
